      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="36973766">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/136486344/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u136486344-11.jpg" alt="Bernard" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36973766/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36973766/" class="">第5页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/136486344/" class=" " title="Bernard">Bernard</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36973766">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“相火由秋降入水中，再由春升上，乃为君火。”火若降于水而复生，则似乎水不能克火。郑钦安说：“天一生水”，天一者，纯阳也。纯阳之火，而能生水，颇为费解。然初学见识浅薄，姑妄存之。俟后深读而有所悟。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-12 21:53</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “相火由秋降入水中，再由春升上，乃为君火。”火若降于水而复生，则似乎水不能克火。郑钦安说：“天一生水”，天一者，纯阳也。纯阳之火，而能生水，颇为费解。然初学见识浅薄，姑妄存之。俟后深读而有所悟。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







